snippet.title: OMORI - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Explore a strange world full of colorful friends and foes as you uncover a forgotten past that will determine your fate... when OMORI comes to Nintendo Switch in Spring 2022!

Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/omori-switch/

#OMORI #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch
